James Rennie (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Rennie_(actor) 0 James Malachi Rennie (April 18, 1889 – July 31, 1965) was a Canadian American actor who performed on the New York stage and also appeared in several Hollywood films during the 1920's, 1930's and 1940's. He became a naturalized as a U.S. citizen in New York in 1933.
